---
title: Carb Smart Tropical Beef Patties with Roasted Sweet Potato and Avocado Salad
description: Bring some island flair to your day with a carb smart meal of Jerk-seasoned beef patties paired with a hearty roasted sweet potato and avocado salad. A sweet and creamy ginger sauce drizzle adds the perfect finishing touch!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/galettes-de-boeuf-tropicales-59ba2f2a.jpg
